      "title": "Protesters enter the Presidential Palace",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The group that traveled along Chatham Street to the President's House entered the President's House at this time.",
        "It is reported that the main entrance to the Presidential Palace was opened and thus entered the Presidential Palace.",
        "The protesters who came on foot along Chatham Street in Colombo reached the main entrance of the President's House a few moments ago.",
        "The protestors who are staying at other places including the struggle ground are approaching the Fort President's House at this time."
